title: 2 men die in crash after Lamborghini crashed in Las Vegas | Daily Mail Online
text: Two men die in fiery crash after losing control of a Lamborghini at the SPEEDVEGAS supercar experience Two men were killed in fiery crash after Lamborghini crashed at SpeedVegas The luxury car burst into flames at motorsports complex in Las Vegas on Sunday A client at SpeedVegas was driving vehicle with an instructor in passenger seat The client, a man in his 30s, lost control of the car around 1.30pm police said Authorities are investigating incident and it's unclear how he lost control of car Published: 03:27 GMT, 13 February 2017 | Updated: 07:26 GMT, 13 February 2017 127 shares
